Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.01,0:00:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.69,0:00:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.20,0:00:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:01:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.33,0:01:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.68,0:01:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not an exit... It's an entrance!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.12,0:02:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heso!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm coming to a stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.47,0:02:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who crashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure does require you to get the hang of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!! You're the coolest!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! This is incredible! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she able to ride that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.69,0:02:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where did Nami-san go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, I wonder if she's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Conis-san, I'm a bit concerned myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here in Skypiea, there's a place that we're\Nnever to step foot in no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never to step foot in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's sacred ground.\N--Sacred ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.19,0:03:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We call that place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Upper Yard, the land where God lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Forbidden Sacred Ground! The Island\NWhere God Lives and Heaven's Judgment!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a God?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a place where we're never to set foot in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes.\N--God... you mean that God?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God lives on the sky island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Since Skypiea is God's Land,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:04:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's ruled by the Almighty God Eneru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Almighty God?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Eneru knows everything in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.21,0:04:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's also watching us all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All the time?!\N--Now, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He's watching us now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph. God, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't believe in God?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. Whether or not\NGod exists doesn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't care less from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't intend to deny\Nthose who want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, have you seen that God who\Nlives in Upper Yard, Conis-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! God forbid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.98,0:04:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot step foot in Upper Yard. Never...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:05:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sacred ground, Upper Yard, is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the sky island has ground, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. A place that we're not\Nallowed to go no matter what, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.61,0:05:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Your eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you thinking about right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen good! "Never step foot in" means
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're absolutely not\Nsupposed to go there, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see... So there's a place\Nthat we're not supposed to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. A place that we're absolutely\Nnot supposed to go, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely planning to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? But if he's God, wouldn't he forgive you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if you go someplace you're\Nnot supposed to? He's nice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... But breaking God's\Nrules is blasphemous, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:06:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Well, I guess it doesn't matter either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because he intends to go\Neven if he won't be forgiven!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what happens if someone goes\Ninto that forbidden Upper Yard?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person cannot come back alive.\NEveryone believes so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cannot come back alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm worried about Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she isn't near Upper Yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami-san!! Stay where you are\N--In any case, let's go there, to find Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--and don't go anywhere!!\N--Is your reason for going really to find Nami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami-san!!\N--Isn't it really so you can\Ngo to the forbidden land?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the huge trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen something this big before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are these trees?\NSeveral hundred years?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All these trees...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see the top of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The treasure should definitely be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An extraordinary treasure is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.39,0:07:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're very close, it's almost within our grasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The treasure is close by! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice came from over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... Hold on a second.\NWe'll go after I finish these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do if\Nsomething happens to Nami-san
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while you're sitting around like it's nothing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave them there,\Nsince we're coming right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... Hold on! This one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conis-chan, it'll be night if I wait for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to that Upper Yard place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we don't know if she was really headed there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if we incur God Eneru's wrath,\Nwe'll really be in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Eneru seems to be pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Eneru... God, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...seems to be on that boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Claw marks...! I wonder if it\Nwas attacked by something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.51,0:08:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The treasure should definitely be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An extraordinary treasure is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're very close...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Th-The seashell is talking!\N--It's almost within our grasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Th-The seashell is talking!\N--The treasure is close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:08:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.86,0:09:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a seashell, right? There's no\Nway there's a human in here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! If we keep a record like this,\Nit may become useful later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this seashell can record voices!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't want to! I'm going back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm scared! I can feel it!\NI can feel God's anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that noise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's God!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By God?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back. It's creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems better to leave this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we're off!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the place we're not allowed to go!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I'm sorry! There's a headwind right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this wind, going to Upper Yard\Nwill take quite long! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Quite long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.01,0:10:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this ship moved using dial energy,\Nit wouldn't take that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:10:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you mean by "quite long"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. Only the wind knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.32,0:11:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I see... Quite long, huh?\N--Old guy! Isn't there any other way
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'd very much like to go,\Nsince I'm worried about Nami.\N--Old guy! Isn't there any other way
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'd very much like to go,\Nsince I'm worried about Nami.\N--to get there quicker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Even I, Usopp-sama, the hero...\N--to get there quicker?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Even I, Usopp-sama, the hero...\N--We'd better hurry, or Nami will be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't control the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! So that was why, after all!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.17,0:11:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--"That"? Which "that"?\N--You liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! That son of a bitch! He took my prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? I can hear noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should, too. He's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.39,0:12:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoho! Same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoho!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What on earth...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on... in this forest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.80,0:12:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's finally a dangerous place we can go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sit around and wait\Ntill the wind changes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:13:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Luffy! Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the old broken waver?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was obviously going to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.12,0:13:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help... me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do? He sank again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're such a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is your old waver.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found it in the sea in the world below.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like me to take a look?\NIf it can be fixed, I'll fix it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can fix it, old guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a dial ship engineer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! Then, please fix it! Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:14:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...do it quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eneru...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.18,0:14:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you want to compete, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind fighting with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to kill my boredom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! That's a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.53,0:14:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to put your\Nbody in this guy's stomach?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hohoho! Small fries crushing each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be a sight! Hoho!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the small fry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.25,0:15:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ride with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.93,0:15:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Err... Ride with me? But this\Nis a one-person boat, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here from another sky\Nisland in search of treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't care about it any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.94,0:15:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can another person ride on this? I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Even if I had to kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guerrilla!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-God...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a bitch! Is this Eneru's doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you harm Vearth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get some Water Dials now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put out the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:34.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Angel Island Lovely Street"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together now, salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heso!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:42.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Captain McKinley\NWhite Berets, Skypiea Police"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heso, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the White Berets!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.39,0:17:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Illegal entrants have infiltrated\NSkypiea through Angel Beach today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.73,0:17:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was reported that there are\Na total of seven infiltrators!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.40,0:18:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the White Berets,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are currently conducting a\Nfull-scale search for these criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.01,0:18:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch out for suspicious individuals!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.68,0:18:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looked like that man\Nwas talking to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a guerrilla. He's just run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.39,0:18:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shut that dog up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.39,0:18:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was probably begging for his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is Eneru-sama thinking,\Ntaking care of that man by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were we...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We probably ran out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran out of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another group of illegal entrants\Nhas already infiltrated this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady Amazon informed us that it's a\Nship with seven Blue Sea people on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven Blue Sea people... Could he mean us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said illegal entrants...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to the upper area,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pay the entrance fee of\None billion Extol per person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.79,0:18:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be because we\Ndidn't pay the entrance fee?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who were riding that boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and, that man, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they entered illegally, they were...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, will the same thing that\Nhappened to that man happen to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no challenge in taking\Ncare of only seven people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven heads... We can't divide them by four.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.46,0:19:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.46,0:19:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell everyone immediately!\NThis place is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Usopp, look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine's finished, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.86,0:20:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check out that art!\NDon't they look just like us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how does that look like us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I think... of your art!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--While Nami-san could be in danger,\Nyou're fooling around!!\N--Stop it! How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take this! And this!\N--Stop it! How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take this! And this!\N--Don't take it out on my art!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Can it be fixed?\N--I've never seen these parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please fix it one way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I can't say much\Nuntil I investigate it more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, please try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try disassembling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.60,0:20:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old guy, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.61,0:20:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, suspicious ship over there, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck are they crawling?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.93,0:21:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably... weirdos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.44,0:21:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! So those are weirdos...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Heso!\N--Heso!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, heso!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, what're you guys saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.96,0:21:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp said they're weirdos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.99,0:21:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the seven illegal entrants\Nwho came from the Blue Sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.66,0:21:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll humbly bring Heaven's Judgment upon you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:22:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, beyond the never-ending sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future that I once saw\Nis now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.66,0:22:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happened, there was\Nsomeplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.55,0:22:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The friends I took pride in\Nalways, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.69,0:22:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pushed me onwards, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.70,0:23:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the stars are pouring\Ndown underneath the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.97,0:23:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This unique moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! That's still only a 5th degree crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.35,0:23:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not good! When it's determined\Nto be a 5th degree crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the name of God Eneru,\Nyou'll be banished to the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Banished to the clouds?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.36,0:23:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Being banished to\Nthe clouds sounds kinda nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't! It's the death penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.39,0:23:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death penalty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.73,0:23:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.06,0:23:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Already Criminals?!\NSkypiea's Upholders of the Law"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
